# =============================================================================
# How to use CODEOWNERS:
# 
# 1. GitHub will automatically request review from code owners when a PR
#    modifies files they own
# 
# 2. You can require code owner review in branch protection rules
# 
# 3. Multiple owners can be specified:
#    /src/ @user1 @user2 @team1
# 
# 4. You can use GitHub teams:
#    /src/ @myorg/team-name
#
